Local golfer Noor Hussain, was the big winner of the Polokwane Pro Shop competition held at PoloÂ­kwane Golf Course on Saturday.
The competition took an individual Stableford format and Hussain finished first with 42 points followed by Jacques Malherbe with 39 points and Joas Legodi who amassed 37 points.
The club announced that they will host Liano Viviers Gold Day tommorow (Friday) and on Saturday stage the Monthly Medal event. Both events will be attended by golfers in Polokwane and sorrounds.
